        <updateDate>2022-10-25T15:48:37Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preventing Abusive Government Efforts Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the federal government from compiling or maintaining a list or other record of federal employees who have requested or been granted a religious exemption or accommodation regarding COVID-19 vaccination requirements. It also requires any such list or record in existence to be destroyed.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
